{
  "texts": [
    "Noise injection: In the most real word, the poor quality of audio may be affected by the old recording device or signal transmission.",
    "We add some white noise to simulate this phenomenon. 3.",
    "Delay: We randomly play the audio back after a period.",
    "Sometimes it may create an echo-like effect, but this does not affect the prediction of sound events. 4.",
    "High/Low pass filters: We apply high/low pass filters for the waveform."
  ]
}